data: Hafsia, Douce, Delphine et Charlotte : quatre jeunes femmes qui cherchent à s’affranchir des limites qu’on voudrait leur imposer. (Hafsia, Douce, Delphine and Charlotte are four young women who seek to overcome the limits that one would like to impose on them.)
Hafsia, Douce, Delphine et Charlotte : quatre jeunes femmes qui cherchent à s’affranchir des limites qu’on voudrait leur imposer.
Hafsia, Douce, Delphine and Charlotte are four young women who seek to overcome the limits that one would like to impose on them.
